"
`;

exports[`full page snapshots kitchen sink (all features) 1`] = `
"# Kitchen Sink

Hello **bold** and ==highlighted== and _italic_ text\\.

Link to [example](https://example.com) and inline \`code()\`\\.

\`\`\`ts
const x: number = 1;
console.log(x);
\`\`\`

\`\`\`py
def hello():
    pass
\`\`\`

> Blockquote with **bold** inside\\.

- Unordered item 1
- Unordered item 2 
  - Nested item

1.  Ordered item 5
2.  Ordered item 6

| Name | Value |
| --- | --- |
| Alpha | 100 |
| Beta | 200 |

---

> [!TIP]
> 
> Tip content here\\.

_Figure caption_

Figure body text\\.

**Author Name**"
`;
